sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant CLI as Wio CLI
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    
    Dev->>CLI: run `wio push`
    CLI->>FS: Read wio.yaml
    FS-->>CLI: Project name
    CLI->>FS: Glob all project files
    FS-->>CLI: List of files
    CLI->>CLI: Bundle into .tar.gz archive
    CLI->>+Network: POST /api/site (FormData: archive + name)
    Note over CLI,Network: Hand-off to Wio Cloud backend
